{"tid":2263062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[今日西朝鮮，明日香港] 中國網民翻牆上《維基百科》被公安上門「查水錶」並公開其姓名和住址","createTime":"2020-10-29T14:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T02:10:54.000Z","uid":155095,"like":59,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"56b7f59c2766a7cb079a7ad6bd3593ccb79b93c4","tid":2263062,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:45:32.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://zh.wikinews.org/wiki/中國網民翻牆上維基百科被處罰\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikinews.org%2Fwiki%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%BF%BB%E7%89%86%E4%B8%8A%E7%B6%AD%E5%9F%BA%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91%E8%A2%AB%E8%99%95%E7%BD%B0&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=6d2b77ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikinews.org/wiki/中國網民翻牆上維基百科被處罰</a><br />\n<br />\n近日，浙江省舟山市一男子被警方查獲。當局指，他使用翻牆軟件「藍燈」在維基百科上搜索資料，被警方上門「查水錶」。消息指，這是中國大陸<strong>首例有人因瀏覽維基百科而被明確處罰的案件</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D7dXnucUYAAKNqV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD7dXnucUYAAKNqV.jpg&h=555cde6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浙江省委官網日前發佈公告稱，該名男子於2019年上半年至今年10月，通過百度搜索翻牆軟件「藍燈」下載安裝後，多次使用翻牆軟件「<span class=\"red\">非法訪問維基百科獲取訊息</span>」，並於24日被警方抓獲，官方公告上亦<span class=\"red\">列出了該名男子的姓名和住址</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://memeprod.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/user-wtf/1586161276251.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmemeprod.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Fuser-wtf%2F1586161276251.jpg&h=9169e4cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有維基百科編者認為，中文維基百科社群應該譴責此事件。公告稱，該名男子的行為構成「<span class=\"red\">擅自建立、使用非法渠道進行國際聯網</span>」的行為，受到行政處罰，當場對該名男子訓誡，並責令其停止連接國際網絡。"},{"pid":"b8b910f1feddecdf352f23542bc8a17fbaa0af34","tid":2263062,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b13eeb33fd364e8eaf295e2bd625119070ed88","tid":2263062,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c231a36abd82fa0739807be26710d7b1eca39707","tid":2263062,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc1be74efa272c480a2bd998ebb3cde0a32afa2","tid":2263062,"uid":151074,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:58:06.000Z","msg":"外國人知唔知支國連上wikipedia都犯法？"},{"pid":"4cc74f22644858ed8de5b97442bd8e6197d5968c","tid":2263062,"uid":173002,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"ccc1be74efa272c480a2bd998ebb3cde0a32afa2","tid":2263062,"uid":151074,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:58:06.000Z","msg":"外國人知唔知支國連上wikipedia都犯法？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T16:07:30.000Z","msg":"香港人應多啲參與維基百科，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家強國上得去搞都係抹黑香港人、灌輸反日反美，為黨散播偽歷史嘅強國網軍。"},{"pid":"23cad0ca27108a4ae6442c16e40dbb2a3383dd10","tid":2263062,"uid":30067,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"ccc1be74efa272c480a2bd998ebb3cde0a32afa2","tid":2263062,"uid":151074,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T15:58:06.000Z","msg":"外國人知唔知支國連上wikipedia都犯法？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T16:45:34.000Z","msg":"唔知<br />\n我同過好多唔同國家既歐洲人<br />\n佢地完全唔知 支那係鎖網"},{"pid":"808e49ec846bbea8fc99bb3ae69dcee45b752d60","tid":2263062,"uid":296677,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"23cad0ca27108a4ae6442c16e40dbb2a338